SPECIAL ACKNOWLEDGMENT:

This library is inspired by and significantly enhanced from the original Beta
library written by Jason Vreeland [CodeRage], released March 7, 2010 under
GNU License. While this current version represents a complete modernization
with industrial-grade features, we acknowledge Jason's pioneering work that
established the foundational concepts for Arduino Modbus RTU implementation.

Enhancements in this version include:

- Non-blocking state machine architecture
- Industrial-grade validation and security
- Atomic transaction protection
- Professional documentation (UML diagrams, flowcharts)
- Extended function code support
- Microsecond-precision RTU timing
- Comprehensive callback system

Enhanced with AI assistance from Google Gemini and GitHub Copilot

